* Iron Raptor saw Prowl come up and take the other side of Dinobot, the 
weight lifting greatly from her shoulders...but he was still heavy.
She walked as quickly as she could, along with Prowl, towards the CR room.
She heard Prowls question, her own voice a bit strained from the effort to 
hold her side of the warrior up.*

" He's not breathing, lungs have failed. Lost all of his fluids, pumps 
running dry. And if we don't get fluid into his body and air into his 
systems soon...he'll die."

* She then checked her internal clock.*

" And we now have 8 minuets to do all that."
